text = "Controller
=========
LStick - Move
RStick - Camera
R3 - Switch Target
Select - Draw/Sheathe
X - Jump
O - Quickstep
[ ] - Interact / Attack
/_\\ - Strong Attack
R1 - Block
R1 -> Lstick - Parry
Quickstep -> R1 - Dash
Dash -> [ ] - Dash Attack
Falling -> [ ] - Falling Attack
"

